f=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109920)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109920)\">Col. 3:22<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109836\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109836)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109836)\">Eph. 5:22-31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}